            </h4>
            <p>Just create an account, log in and visit any subdomain of klavado.com (for example <a href="http://joy.klavado.com">http://joy.klavado.com</a> ).  If that subdomain has not been claimed by anyone else, you can claim if for yourself by filling in two fields.   </p>
